public static class AntPluginPcc.RequestAccessResultHandler<T extends AntPluginPcc>
extends Handler

Used to define how the request access results are handled. This base class handles reporting the results of SUCCESS, and the errors DEPENDENCYNOTINSTALLED, OTHERFAILURE, USERCANCELLED, and CHANNELNOTAVAILABLE.
